Package net.sf.jguiraffe.gui.platform.swing.builder.components.table

Class AbstractTableModelTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jguiraffe.gui.platform.swing.builder.components.table.AbstractTableModelTest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TestSwingSelectionHandler, TestSwingTableCellEditor, TestSwingTableCellRenderer
    public abstract class AbstractTableModelTest
extends Object
    An abstract test class for tests of Swing table functionality. This class provides common functionality for setting up a table model, a table tag and more.
    Version:
    $Id: AbstractTableModelTest.java 205 2012-01-29 18:29:57Z oheger $
    Author:
    Oliver Heger

        Fully initializes a table tag for the test table based on the provided parameters.
        Parameters:
        data - the data collection; can be null, then default data will be created
        width - if set to true, the widths of the columns are set
        scrollWidth - the scroll width as string (can be null)
        scrollHeight - the scroll height as string (can be null)
        Returns:
        the initialized tag
